            <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-white/80">
              Book a free 15-minute discovery call with a friendly wealth expert. We will answer your doubts, help you understand your risk comfort, and show you how a dedicated advisor can fast-track your wealth creation.
